          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Volunteer Driver Tax Appreciation Act of 2019</b></p> <p>This bill increases the standard mileage rate for the tax deduction for the charitable use of a passenger automobile. The bill increases the rate from the standard charitable rate of 14 cents per mile to the standard business mileage rate (58 cents per mile for 2019). </p>]]></text>
